name: Mash Attack - Learn and Evolve
description:
Mash Attack's debut E.P. consists of five tracks transcending borders of old school ska and progressive rock, creating a blend of organized punk. It's something to chill out to before bed, rock out in your car to or for power walking down the street, especially if you're holding a poodle on a leash! 

Track Listing:

Old Friend
Weight On Your Mind
Man Down
Baby Girl
